_:Nf5d13b7036784119ae62e35cef354e80 <http://schema.org/description> "The Fire Service College (FSC) supplies specialist fire and rescue training to the UK’s own fire and rescue services, the private security sector and the international market. The college was formerly an executive agency of the Department for Communities and Local Government and was sold to Capita on 28 February 2013." .
